{"tid":1962594,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［底已起］鏗鏘集學生妹j圖","createTime":"2020-04-07T14:32:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-08T15:43:57.000Z","uid":302,"like":149,"dislike":114,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"635ba2e6b3e4135179ccf3fc1e01f6b5f8b08677","tid":1962594,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T14:32:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://g.udn.com.tw/upfiles/B_EN/energy7429/PSN_PHOTO/688/f_12342688_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fg.udn.com.tw%2Fupfiles%2FB_EN%2Fenergy7429%2FPSN_PHOTO%2F688%2Ff_12342688_1.jpg&h=4cec42ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcRX9ITyC_HITaVT9qYNVh9gxCoPX0T8rsl_Gg3m-EwpHYLwwmX7&amp;usqp=CAU\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%253AANd9GcRX9ITyC_HITaVT9qYNVh9gxCoPX0T8rsl_Gg3m-EwpHYLwwmX7%26usqp%3DCAU&h=ae06e8ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n成班咸濕仔 睇不淨觀啦 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 由戒j開始</span></span>"},{"pid":"7d75e16acebf47da1268e5632d080a0578f1b265","tid":1962594,"uid":302,"like":7,"dislike":7,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T14:33:09.000Z","msg":"#迷了就看真相 #不淨觀 #文殊菩薩除淫慾咒 #文殊菩薩 #除淫慾咒 #youtube #咒 #文殊菩薩 #除淫慾咒<br />\n<br />\n&quot;給大家兩個親測最有效也是一直在用的應急方法：<br />\n<br />\n1.<br />\n<br />\n文殊菩薩除淫慾咒。<br />\n<br />\n咒很短，幾十個字，但是效果非常強烈，讀幾遍就有效果，讀 21 遍會有很明顯的效果。<br />\n<br />\n應急的時候，讀這個非常好，大家可以存成圖片，放在手機上。<br />\n<br />\n有幾次破戒，都是這個咒幫我迅速熄滅了慾火。<br />\n<br />\n注意，讀楞嚴咒、抄寫僧伽吒經、讀文殊菩薩除淫慾咒，都需要回向，我會把所有需要的資料打包一下發出來，各位存手機裡就可以了，非常方便。<br />\n<br />\n2.<br />\n<br />\n不淨觀視頻。<br />\n<br />\n隨時存手機裡，慾望一來，看幾秒，就能立刻把你從迷的狀態中解救出來，因為這個視頻展示的就是真相，迷了就看真相，自然能很快覺悟過來。<br />\n<br />\n慾望本就是迷的產物，覺悟了，慾望馬上就消失了。<br />\n<br />\n【順便提一句，實踐是檢驗真理的唯一標準。<br />\n<br />\n實實在在去行動一次，比什麼都有說服力。】&quot;<br />\n<br />\n文殊菩薩除淫欲咒唱誦版<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nBUyBlBdnDI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DnBUyBlBdnDI&d=BHyrWEjohbhGCquuSPOYYpNY2w26zYPSLCKwhaLFqs8%3D&h=12b92a44\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nBUyBlBdnDI</a><br />\n<br />\n戒撸白骨观（飞翔出品） 标清<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8aJz6R9j8CU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D8aJz6R9j8CU&d=BHyrWEjohbhGCquuSPOYYpNY2w26zYPSLCKwhaLFqs8%3D&h=3b8dfc56\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8aJz6R9j8CU</a>"},{"pid":"5521bd02f1846f80fed020f26bdc2d93559b5bca","tid":1962594,"uid":302,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T14:33:38.000Z","msg":"首先，各位比較新入黎，我簡單解釋一下呢個谷。<br />\n其實性上癮既問題比想像中嚴重好多，因為網絡世界色情文化泛濫，令到好多後生仔打丁打到身體岀現問題，而中醫說法黎講，打丁打到腎虧，更會衍生岀好多不同既身體問題，包括，腎痛，尿頻，耳嗚，失眠，抑鬱，等等。<br />\n<br />\n西方亦有學者對性上癮患者進行研究，以下，係腦神經科學家解釋性上癮對腦部做成影響既短片。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/78fP7uMY-KU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F78fP7uMY-KU&d=BHyrWEjohbhGCquuSPOYYpNY2w26zYPSLCKwhaLFqs8%3D&h=0b4756cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/78fP7uMY-KU</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n由於社會缺乏正式學習戒色脫癮及養生知識既渠道，世界各地都有自發性既網絡戒色團體，包括外國英文既 Nofap, 內地既戒色吧，麥田男孩，而香港亦有規模比較小既Real life group。<br />\n<br />\n腦部上癮既模式大致上都相似。 <br />\n喺當今禍害人最深既 [黃，賭，毒]，三者入面，政府對戒賭和戒毒都有正式既機構去協助脫癮，而可惜對色情產業所帶來的負面影響並沒有很多正式的協助及宣傳。<br />\n<br />\n養生練好身體，鍛鍊好自己堅定既意志，不再受到誘惑，不再懼怕。<br />\n<br />\n[ It is impossible to heal the body without healing the soul. ]-Socrates<br />\n<br />\n身心為一體。<br />\n擁有鋼鐵般的意志，就會有鋼鐵般的身體。<br />\nStep out of comfort zone. <br />\nFight for the best.<br />\n共勉之。<br />\n🔥🔥🔥🔥🔥🔥🔥🔥🔥🔥🔥<br />\n<br />\n假設心魔等級100，你定力等級只有15，你怎麼能和心魔抗衡？<br />\n記住，唔睇文只係等破戒<br />\n<br />\n想戒丁成功就要睇哂《戒為良藥》<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.qiusuoo.com/2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.qiusuoo.com%2F2&d=BHyrWEjohbhGCquuSPOYYpNY2w26zYPSLCKwhaLFqs8%3D&h=14250336\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.qiusuoo.com/2</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[我諗可能都要pin 一pin呢樣嘢，<br />\n<br />\n有好多巴打好鐘意每日喺到叫day0，對自己其實冇乜好處，冇乜幫助，喺心理層面又會覺得自己好冇用，持續下去其實有機會變成一個負面既循環，就係而家社會運動成日講既{失敗主義}。<br />\n<br />\n與其叫day 0,不如搵啲戒色養生既知識文章 post 上group,等各位巴打谷友都可以溫故而知新。而其他巴打受到感染，可能就會一齊講戒色養生既知識，互相學習，形成一個正向既feedback cycle🔄<br />\n<br />\n持續既努力學習知識，絕對比持續地大叫自己 day0 有用得多，<br />\n算是正向思考的一種。]<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n#全民運動 #全民皆兵 <br />\n#光復香港 #時代革命"},{"pid":"92ed111dc9812a9765483d0f57a54ed4ac42b3cb","tid":1962594,"uid":245670,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T14:34:03.000Z","msg":"Day0<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11fff96a8fb1f879db2fad22a48ae43b5251b918","tid":1962594,"uid":94828,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T14:34:18.000Z","msg":"睇完副骨扯咗<br />\n縮唔返點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a96882ae422ed99071fb7d8e9cb191795533f46","tid":1962594,"uid":302,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"92ed111dc9812a9765483d0f57a54ed4ac42b3cb","tid":1962594,"uid":245670,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T14:34:03.000Z","msg":"Day0<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T14:34:24.000Z","msg":"召喚蕭別離<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33d80e65258696caccc62e5f2b1e55c85d9fcd03","tid":1962594,"uid":63311,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T14:34:28.000Z","msg":"做多左"},{"pid":"fca6f4659c2d6307f423ccded3d30fa631231c20","tid":1962594,"uid":220853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T14:36:04.000Z","msg":"扯左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"570d72e3aaab20f2a5acf19da9c9b6abc92910d5","tid":1962594,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T14:36:16.000Z","msg":"未來人KFK:<br />\n因為中國己經開始新的階段, 我不能逗留, 故回覆你們的答覆亦不完整。<br />\n1. 只能說是意識体, 但是你的5感是無法察覺他們。<br />\n2. 歷史是不可人為改變, 這是我們的根本法則。<br />\n3. 每人理解宗教的定義不同, 我們那年人心赤露,萬宗歸一, 精神層面有一個新的功能, 還未被大部份人試著開啓。在我的年代, 大家都摒棄物質而深造精神方面的昇華是原因之一。<br />\n4.獅身人面像的事, 答案好像是在地底吧，它將會是一個推使我們走入精神層面的大門。<br />\n5.人位 是我們那年代的用語, 指位置(精神上的階段)<br />\n6. 這個媒體, 在我小學時還存在的。 素食和提昇精神領域是個很好的題目, 要我說嘛, 盡力創作將會為你帶來意想不到的收穫。<br />\n7. 像你看萬花筒一樣。<br />\n8. 抱歉這個我不能說, 因為歷史會隨之改變。<br />\n<br />\n你一直有做meditation, 它將會為你帶來更多的啓示。這是一條開啓的鎖匙。<br />\n<br />\n戒丁可能是光復香港關鍵😃"},{"pid":"d52dc3812ae21bcc57626d98db101c42e0552b76","tid":1962594,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T14:38:04.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d50366bf0ffc5c576a43311e4142535a7de29a2","tid":1962594,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"33d80e65258696caccc62e5f2b1e55c85d9fcd03","tid":1962594,"uid":63311,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T14:34:28.000Z","msg":"做多左"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T14:39:19.000Z","msg":"要幫手足深層潔淨"},{"pid":"8c368d83c6842f4d299c948850304d5ddf28ebb1","tid":1962594,"uid":8500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T14:39:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0a361d42c87a17e81f5a6420e21f1d9998c6ba2","tid":1962594,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c368d83c6842f4d299c948850304d5ddf28ebb1","tid":1962594,"uid":8500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T14:39:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T14:41:34.000Z","msg":"千萬唔好係google搜 不淨觀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b5abd15abcb5f6b1a5034edcac428b715a76c9d",